      <SectionShell id="primary-tools" title="Core Flywheel Tools">
        <TldrToolGrid tools={primaryTools} />
      </SectionShell>

      <SectionShell id="supporting-tools" title="Supporting Tools">
        <TldrToolGrid tools={supportingTools} />
      </SectionShell>
    </main>
  );
}
```

## Implementation Notes
- Server component where possible
- Pass data to client components
- Use existing SectionShell for consistency
- Add smooth scroll targets for navigation

## Dependencies
- Requires: All UI components built
- Requires: tldr-data.ts complete
- Blocks: Testing and polish

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Route accessible at /tldr
