# Mobile Bottom Sheet for Tool Details

## Overview
Replace inline card expansion with a bottom sheet modal on mobile devices. This provides a better mobile UX by not pushing content around and giving more room for details.

## Problem with Current Approach
- Expanding a card pushes all content below it down
- User loses context of where they were in the grid
- Expanded content is cramped in card width
- Difficult to compare tools (can only expand one at a time)

## Proposed Solution
On mobile (< 768px), clicking "Show More" opens a bottom sheet that:
- Slides up from bottom
- Contains full tool details
- Has close button and swipe-to-dismiss
- Leaves card grid visible but dimmed behind

## Design Specifications

### Bottom Sheet Anatomy
