```

### Interaction States
- **Opening**: Slides up with spring physics
- **Open**: ~80% viewport height, scrollable content
- **Dismissing**: Swipe down past threshold or tap backdrop
- **Closed**: Slides down, backdrop fades

## Technical Implementation

### Using Framer Motion
```tsx
function ToolBottomSheet({ tool, isOpen, onClose }) {
  return (
    <AnimatePresence>
      {isOpen && (
        <>
          {/* Backdrop */}
          <motion.div
            initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
            animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
            exit={{ opacity: 0 }}
            onClick={onClose}
            className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 z-50"
          />

          {/* Sheet */}
          <motion.div
            initial={{ y: '100%' }}
            animate={{ y: 0 }}
            exit={{ y: '100%' }}
            transition={{ type: 'spring', damping: 25, stiffness: 300 }}
            drag="y"
            dragConstraints={{ top: 0, bottom: 0 }}
            dragElastic={0.2}
            onDragEnd={(_, info) => {
              if (info.offset.y > 100 || info.velocity.y > 500) {
                onClose();
              }
            }}
            className="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 max-h-[85vh] rounded-t-3xl bg-slate-900 overflow-hidden"
          >
            {/* Drag handle */}
            <div className="sticky top-0 bg-slate-900 pt-3 pb-2">
              <div className="mx-auto h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-slate-700" />
            </div>

            {/* Content */}
            <div className="overflow-y-auto px-6 pb-8">
              {/* Tool details here */}
            </div>
          </motion.div>
        </>
      )}
    </AnimatePresence>
  );
}
```

### Responsive Integration
```tsx
// In TldrToolCard
const isMobile = useMediaQuery('(max-width: 767px)');
const [sheetOpen, setSheetOpen] = useState(false);

// Different behavior based on viewport
const handleExpand = () => {
  if (isMobile) {
    setSheetOpen(true);
  } else {
    onToggleExpand?.(); // Original inline expansion
  }
};
```

## Files to Create/Modify
- `components/tool-bottom-sheet.tsx` (new) - Bottom sheet component
- `components/tldr-tool-card.tsx` - Conditional expansion behavior
- `hooks/use-media-query.ts` (if not exists) - Media query hook

## Accessibility
- Focus trap when sheet is open
- Escape key closes sheet
- `aria-modal="true"` on sheet
- Return focus to trigger button on close
- Backdrop click closes (with visual indication)

## Performance
- Lazy load sheet content (only render when opening)
- Use `will-change: transform` for smooth animation
- Portal to document.body to escape stacking contexts

## Acceptance Criteria
