# Enhanced Card Hover Choreography

## Overview
Elevate the tool card hover states to Stripe-level polish with staggered, choreographed animations where different elements animate in sequence.

## Current State
- Basic opacity change on gradient background
- Simple border color transition
- Ring appears on expanded state
- Spotlight follows cursor (good foundation)

## Proposed Choreography

### Hover Sequence (Desktop)
```
T+0ms:   Border lightens (0.1 ‚Üí 0.2 opacity)
T+30ms:  Gradient background intensifies (0.05 ‚Üí 0.12 opacity)  
T+50ms:  Icon container lifts slightly (translateY -2px)
T+80ms:  Card shadow deepens and spreads
T+100ms: Spotlight effect reaches full intensity
```

### Hover Exit Sequence
- Reverse order, slightly faster (0.8x duration)
- Maintains perceived smoothness

## Technical Implementation

### Using CSS Transitions with Delays
```css
.tool-card {
  /* Base transitions with staggered delays on hover */
  .border-element { transition: border-color 150ms ease-out; }
  .gradient-bg { transition: opacity 150ms ease-out 30ms; }
  .icon-container { transition: transform 200ms cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) 50ms; }
  .card-shadow { transition: box-shadow 250ms ease-out 80ms; }
}

.tool-card:hover {
  .border-element { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .gradient-bg { opacity: 0.12; }
  .icon-container { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .card-shadow { box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
}

/* Faster exit - remove delays */
.tool-card:not(:hover) {
  .border-element { transition-delay: 60ms; }
  .gradient-bg { transition-delay: 40ms; }
  .icon-container { transition-delay: 20ms; }
  .card-shadow { transition-delay: 0ms; }
}
```

### Using Framer Motion
```tsx
const cardVariants = {
  rest: {
    borderColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)',
    transition: { duration: 0.2, ease: 'easeOut' }
  },
  hover: {
    borderColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)',
    transition: { duration: 0.15, ease: 'easeOut' }
  }
};

const iconVariants = {
  rest: { y: 0 },
  hover: { 
    y: -2,
    transition: { 
      type: 'spring',
      stiffness: 400,
      damping: 17,
      delay: 0.05
    }
  }
};
```

