## Performance Considerations
- Use `will-change: transform, opacity` sparingly
- Prefer CSS transitions over Framer Motion for simple properties
- Avoid animating box-shadow directly (use pseudo-element)
- Test on low-end devices

## Reduced Motion
- Disable choreography delays (all at once)
- Keep color/opacity changes (instant)
- Remove transform animations entirely

